{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"84dee5afea","title":"陈伯达和首都职工造反派代表座谈纪录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbf5a024a7","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"84dee5afea","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"王力","id":"20ebde32a6","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘建勋","id":"3ae36abefb","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢镗忠","id":"70f74b01a1","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"余秋里","id":"a5ef5c1d16","type":"人物"},{"name":"谷牧","id":"b28bc58f9a","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"},{"name":"唐平铸","id":"f22ee87d49","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"476478f9ce","type":"title","text":"陈伯达和首都职工造反派代表座谈纪录","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9fb97e3d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"〖参加座谈会的有：首都职工红色革命造反总联络站等单位五十馀名工人代表，姚文元、戚本禹、王力、余秋里、唐平铸、高扬文、刘建勋、谢镗忠、谷牧等。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e41f4e471","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：同志们，今天来开个座谈会，今天主要靠你们来谈谈工厂的文化大革命怎么搞，我们是来当小学生的，我们小组人力很少，对工厂的情况了解很少，我们是勤务员，没当好！大家问工厂的文化大革命怎么搞，我们在整个文化大革命中，对工矿企业的工作做得很少。工厂究竟怎样搞法，存在什么问题，过去我们搞得很少，有意见也没有很好研究，今天的会是个开端。大家提些问题，我们带回去。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40f218e105","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：大家提提有什么问题，大家提。各种意见和要求都可以讲，今天开不完，明天还可以开。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b06a6d2a82","type":"paragraph","text":"（光华木材厂，机床厂，起重机厂，内燃机厂等代表发言）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fad8d00eed","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：今天就谈到这里。明天我们不要这样发言。是不是谈谈大家都关心的事，就是咱们怎样贯彻好十六条，怎样贯彻好。工厂组织怎样办好。有的要成立全市性的组织，要不要？怎么搞好？有的对<人民日报>社论有点意见，有什么都可以谈。我们是当小学生的，听取群众的意见。各厂情况可以写材料，可以写信，寄给中央文革，我们就可以收到。明天三点继续开。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eafc4586b7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：明天还有事。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78d2513d9a","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：开会先不定，再开另通知。怎么开好，大家可以提意见。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b847a5b0b3","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：什么时间开，另行通知。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"39398017a5","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：今天晚上有会，就谈到这里。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e831dd821","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志回答问题：","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66120a6495","type":"paragraph","text":"问：成立全市工人造反司令部，有人说我们是非法的。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9ac52a838","type":"paragraph","text":"答：不要成立什么司令部，成立个什么红卫兵代表大会呀，什么联合会呀！司令部本身就有司令，总指挥……司令部本身就有点衙门性质。红卫兵搞个什么游行，开个什么大会，可以临时选出个总指挥。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aca43c381b","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：他们可能是从大专三个司令部那里学来的。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0925ca9a80","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：要学习革命学生的好的经验，不要搞宗派，首先开个联席会，大家商量商量。首先创造出一个典型，起模范带头作用，抓革命促生产。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae55a10a41","type":"paragraph","text":"问：市委对工人运动很冷谈，怎么办？","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2a09d6731","type":"paragraph","text":"答：那个不对。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ad04e5a6f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：学生到工厂很困难。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ff2d5f5b7","type":"paragraph","text":"答：进去做工人的学生。我是你们的学生，小小的学生，我们是劳动人民的儿子，我们向你们学习。今天的讲话，是和你们商量的。我们要执行毛主席的指示，抓革命促生产，要把生产搞得更好，要超过世界上所有的先进的国家，不许把生产停下来。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e5661473e","type":"paragraph","text":"问：在文化大革命中被打成“反革命”、“牛鬼蛇神”，开除的怎么办？","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"341bec631b","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：开除的，中央有指示，都算无效，过去凡是打成\"反革命\"的一律无效。黑材料一律烧掉。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd5aac1175","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：一律当众烧掉。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b60394da88","type":"paragraph","text":"问：有的他们偷偷地烧掉了，怎么办？","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7d3963db2","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：偷偷烧掉要做检查。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bc5c80dec","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他交出来，又保存一份，怎么办？","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b87b4ca4c","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：保存起来就犯错误，就违反了国家纪律，党的纪律。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b7b3d4be4","type":"paragraph","text":"问：有的不给，放在档案室里，是否可以砸？","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"993b0c7f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：不给吗？要革命，要斗争，最好不要砸。中央新的指示即将发下来，希望你们按中央指示办事。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d80aa283a","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：时间不早了，我们还有个会，就谈到这里。再见！","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"84dee5afea","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}